{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-220-heighway-dragon","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 220: Heighway Dragon","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je $D_0$ niz od dva znaka \"Fa\". Za $n ≥ 1$, napravite $D_n$ od $D_{n - 1}$ koristeći pravila za prepisivanje niza znakova:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\"a\" → \"aRbFR\"</li>\n<li>\"b\" → \"LFaLb\"</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dakle, $D_0$ = \"Fa\", $D_1$ = \"FaRbFR\", $D_2$ = \"FaRbFRRLFaLbFR\", i tako dalje.</p>\n<p>Ovaj niz se može tumačiti kao instrukcije za program računarske grafike, gde \"F\" znači \"crtaj napred za jedan korak\", \"L\" znači \"okreni levo za 90 stepeni\", \"R\" znači \"okreni desno za 90 stepeni\", a \"a\" i \"b\" se ignorišu. Početna pozicija računarskog kursorа je (0,0), a smer je gore ka (0,1).</p>\n<p>Zatim, $D_n$ je jedinstveni crtež poznat kao Heighway Dragon nivoa $n$. Na primer, $D_{10}$ je prikazan ispod; računajući svako \"F\" kao jedan korak, deo označen bojom na (18,16) je pozicija dosegnuta nakon koraka 500.</p>\n<img alt=\"drawing of the Heighway Dragon after 500 steps\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/heighway-dragon.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Koja je pozicija računarskog kursora nakon koraka ${10}^{12}$ u $D_{50}$? Napišite odgovor kao niz znakova u formatu <code>x,y</code> bez razmaka.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4481000cf542c50ff5b","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301863,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-220-heighway-dragon"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function heighwayDragon() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nheighwayDragon();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>heighwayDragon()</code> trebao bi vratiti sekvencu karaktera.</p>","testString":"assert.isString(heighwayDragon());"},{"text":"<p><code>heighwayDragon()</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>139776,963904</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(heighwayDragon(), '139776,963904');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-220-heighway-dragon","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-221-alexandrian-integers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-219-skew-cost-coding","id":"5900f4481000cf542c50ff5b","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-220-heighway-dragon"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}